{"name": "linkml-owl", "metadata": {"name": "linkml-owl", "version": "0.4.2", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 4 - Beta", "Environment :: Console", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "Intended Audience :: Healthcare Industry", "Intended Audience :: Science/Research", "License :: CC0 1.0 Universal (CC0 1.0) Public Domain Dedication", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3 :: Only", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.7", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.8", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9"], "home_page": "https://github.com/linkml/linkml-owl", "license": null, "documentation_url": "https://github.com/linkml/linkml-owl", "dependencies": ["Jinja2", "click", "funowl", "linkml", "linkml-runtime"], "summary": "OWL mappings for Linked Open Data Modeling Language", "upload_time": 1717091736}, "documentation": ["# linkml-owl\n\nTranslates between LinkML instance data to OWL (TBoxes and ABoxes)\n\nSee [linkml.io/linkml-owl](https://linkml.io/linkml-owl/)\n\n\n"], "modules": [{"name": "linkml_owl.crossproducts", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "linkml_owl", "documentation": ["use importlib.metadata to read the version provided", "by the package during installation. Do not hardcode", "the version in the code"], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "linkml_owl.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "linkml_owl.dumpers", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "linkml_owl.crossproducts.cross_product_generator", "documentation": ["Cross-Product Generator\n\nFor any instance a that has an xp declaration:\n\n1. compute all instances G=i1..in that are reachable from a over xp.propagates_over\n2. for each i in combination of i1..in, crea