 dict.\n\nAll objects created will be of type target_class; if this is not specified, then it may be inferred:\n\n- if the schema specified a tree_root, this is used\n- if the objects contain a type designator, this is used\n\n```\nparam source\n\npath or data or stream\n\nparam target_class\n\nclass to be instantiated, either name or the python class\n\nparam fmt\n\nAny of yaml, json, csv, ttl. inferred if None and source is a file path\n\nparam python_module\n\npython module for datamodel classes\n\nparam schema\n\n\n\nparam schemaview\n\nrequired if the input is CSV or RDF\n\nreturn\n\nEither a single LinkML object OR a list of them\n```\n"]}, {"name": "linkml_owl.util.loader_wrapper.instantiate_object", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "data", "type": {"name": "Dict", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Dict", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "target_class", "type": {"name": "Type", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Type", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "YAMLRoot", "xref": {"fqname": "linkml_runtime.utils.yamlutils.YAMLRoot", "project": "linkml-runtime"}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "schemaview", "type": {"name": "SchemaView", "xref": {"fqname": "linkml_runtime.SchemaView", "project": "linkml-runtime"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "type_designator", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "python_module", "type": {"name": "ModuleType", "xref": {"fqname": "types.ModuleType", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "YAMLRoot", "xref": {"fqname": "linkml_runtime.utils.yamlutils.YAMLRoot", "project": "linkml-runtime"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "linkml_owl.util.loader_wrapper.get_type_designator", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "schemaview", "type": {"name": "SchemaView", "xref": {"fqname": "linkml_runtime.SchemaView", "project": "l