"xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "**args", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Dump LinkML instance data as OWL\n\nExamples:\n\nConvert a CSV to OWL\n\n    linkml-data2owl -s owl_dumper_test.yaml parts.csv -o parts.ofn\n\nNote in this example, there must be a class type designator column `@type` in the CSV\n\nConvert a CSV to OWL, homogeneous classes:\n\n    linkml-data2owl -C EquivGenusAndPartOf -s owl_dumper_test.yaml             parts_implicit_type.csv -o parts.ofn\n\nConvert YAML or JSON to OWL:\n\n    linkml-data2owl -s owl_dumper_test.yaml owl_dumper_test_data.yaml -o ont.ofn\n\nMore documentation:\n\n    https://linkml.io/linkml-owl/"]}], "variables": [{"name": "linkml_owl.dumpers.owl_dumper.INTERPRETATION", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "linkml_owl.dumpers.owl_dumper.AXIOM_TYPE_NAME", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "linkml_owl.dumpers.owl_dumper.OPERAND", "type": null, "documentation": ["# e.g IntersectionOf, UnionOf"]}, {"name": "linkml_owl.dumpers.owl_dumper.LEVEL", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "linkml_owl.dumpers.owl_dumper.OP_KEY", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "linkml_owl.dumpers.owl_dumper.EntityAxiomIndex", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "linkml_owl.dumpers.owl_dumper.EntityAxiomIndex.add_operand", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "key", "type": {"name": "OP_KEY", "xref": {"fqname": "OP_KEY", "project": null}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "op", "type": {"name": "ClassExpression", "xref": {"fqname": "funowl.ClassExpression", "project": "funowl"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "anns", "type": {"name": "List", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.List", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "Annotation", "xref": {"fqname": "funowl.Annotation", "project": "funowl"}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Adds to part of an index\n\n```\nparam key\n\ncombo of operator/axiomType/level\n\nparam op\n\noperand - an element of the list used to construct the operator construct\n\nreturn\n\n```\n"]}, {"name": "linkml_owl.dumpers.owl_dumper.EntityAxiomIndex.add_operands", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "key", "type": {"name": "OP_KEY", "xref": {"fqname": "OP_KEY", "project": null}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "ops", "type": {"name": "List", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.List", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "ClassExpression", "xref": {"fqname": "funowl.ClassExpression", "project": "funowl"}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}, {"name": "anns", "type": {"name": "List", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.List", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "Annotation", "xref": {"fqname": "funowl.Annotation", "project": "funowl"}, "params": null}]}, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Adds to part of an index\n\n```\nparam key\n\n\n\nparam ops\n\n\n\nparam anns\n\n\n\nreturn\n\n```\n"]}], "class_variables": [{"name": "linkml_owl.dumpers.owl_dumper.EntityAxiomIndex.operand_list_index", "type": {"name": "Dict", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Dict", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "OP_KEY", "xref": {"fqname": "OP_KEY", "project": null}, "params": null}, {"name": "List", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.List", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "ClassExpression", "xref": {"fqname": "funowl.ClassExpression", "project": "funowl"}, "params": null}]}]}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "linkml_owl.dumpers.owl_dumper.EntityAxiomIndex.annotation_list_index", "type": {"name": "Dict", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Dict", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "OP_KEY", "xref": {"fqname": "OP_KEY", "project": null}, "params": null}, {"name": "List", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.List", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "Annotation", "xref": {"fqname": "funowl.Annotation", "project": "funowl"}, "params": null}]}]}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "linkml_owl.dumpers.owl_dumper.EntityAxiomIndex.annotations", "type": {"name": "List", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.List", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "Annotation", "xref": {"fqname": "funowl.Annotation", "project": "funowl"}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "linkml_owl.dumpers.owl_dumper.EntityAxiomIndex.object_index", "type": {"name": "ObjectIndex", "xref": {"fqname": "linkml_runtime.index.object_index.ObjectIndex", "project": "linkml-runtime"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["An index of axioms (plus annotations), indexed by entity, plus aggregate grouping criteria (intersection, union)\n\nMotivation: any entity (such as a class) might have an arbitrary number of equivalence, disjointness, etc axioms\nassociated with it; e.g.\n\n```pycon\n>>> A = B or C\n>>> A = D and E\n>>> A SubClassOf F or G\n>>>       ...\n```\n\nThis index allows these axioms to be incrementally constructed\n\nThe index is via a tripartite key (OP_KEY) with elements:\n\n- Operator (e.g. AND/IntersectionOf, OR/Union)\n- AxiomType (e.g. SubClassOf, EquivalentClasses)\n- Level (default 0), allows for example multiple equivalence axioms using intersection\n"]}, {"name": "linkml_owl.dumpers.owl_dumper.OWLDumper", "bases": ["Dumper"], "methods": [{"name": "linkml_owl.dumpers.owl_dumper.OWLDumper.to_ontology_document", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "element", "type": {"name": "Union", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Union", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "YAMLRoot", "xref": {"fqname": "linkml_runtime.utils.yamlutils.YAMLRoot", "project": "linkml-runtime"}, "params": null}, {"name": "List", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.List", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "YAMLRoot", "xref": {"fqname": "linkml_runtime.utils.yamlutils.YAMLRoot", "project": "linkml-runtime"}, "params": null}]}]}, "default": null}, {"name": "schema", "type": {"name": "Union", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Union", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "SchemaDefinition", "xref": {"fqname": "linkml_runtime.linkml_model.meta.SchemaDefinition", "project": "linkml-runtime"}, "params": null}, {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}, {"name": "iri", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "OntologyDocument", "xref": {"fqname": "funowl.OntologyDocument", "project": "funowl"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Recursively convert a linkml instance tree to an OWL Ontology Document\n\n```\nparam element\n\nelement to convert\n\nparam schema\n\n\n\nparam iri\n\n\n\nreturn\n\n```\n"]}, {"name": "linkml_owl.dumpers.owl_dumper.OWLDumper.dumps", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "element", "type": {"name": "YAMLRoot", "xref": {"fqname": "linkml_runtime.utils.yamlutils.YAMLRoot", "project": "linkml-runtime"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "schema", "type": {"name": "SchemaDefinition", "xref": {"fqname": "linkml_runtime.linkml_model.meta.SchemaDefinition", "project": "linkml-runtime"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "schemaview", "type": {"name": "SchemaView", "xref": {"fqname": "linkml_runtime.SchemaView", "project": "linkml-runtime"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "iri", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "output_type", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Dump a linkml instance tree to a function syntax OWL ontology string\n\n```\nparam element\n\n\n\nparam schema\n\n\n\nparam schemaview\n\n\n\nparam iri\n\n\n\nparam output_type\n\n\n\nreturn\n\n```\n"]}, {"name": "linkml_owl.dumpers.owl_dumper.OWLDumper.transform", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "element", "type": {"name": "YAMLRoot", "xref": {"fqname": "linkml_runtime.utils.yamlutils.YAMLRoot", "project": "linkml-runtime"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "schema", "type": {"name": "SchemaDefinition", "xref": {"fqname": "linkml_runtime.linkml_model.meta.SchemaDefinition", "project": "linkml-runtime"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "is_element_an_object", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Recursively transform a LinkML element\n\nEach field is introspected, and translated to an OWL axiom or expression.\nThe field value is recursively transformed\n\n```\nparam element\n\n\n\nparam schema\n\n\n\nparam is_element_an_object\n\n\n\nparam is_element_an_owl_class\n\n\n\nreturn\n\nIRI or node of transformation of element\n```\n"]}, {"name": "linkml_owl.dumpers.owl_dumper.OWLDumper.add_axiom", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "axiom", "type": {"name": "Axiom", "xref": {"fqname": "funowl.Axiom", "project": "funowl"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "ontology", "type": {"name": "Ontology", "xref": {"fqname": "funowl.Ontology", "project": "funowl"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "axiom_annotations", "type": {"name": "List", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.List", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "Annotation", "xref": {"fqname": "funowl.Annotation", "project": "funowl"}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Add an axiom to the ontology, appending any annotations to the axiom.\n\n```\nparam axiom\n\n\n\nparam ontology\n\n\n\nparam axiom_ann